translation: Zero! Hey! Hey, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero! Hey! Hey, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: *Sigh* Look, why don't you take to the{LF}skies and look for One and Three, okay?{#Name="Zero"}
source: *Sigh* Look, why don't you take to the{LF}skies and look for One and Three, okay?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Awww! Why? You don't like being with me?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Awww! Why? You don't like being with me?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Is it because I smell? Is that it?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Is it because I smell? Is that it?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What? No! I...just want to see you spread your{LF}wings and soar across the skies! ...And stuff.{#Name="Zero"}
source: What? No! I...just want to see you spread your{LF}wings and soar across the skies! ...And stuff.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, really? Wow! Okay, you got it!{LF}Watch this, all right? Watch this!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh, really? Wow! Okay, you got it!{LF}Watch this, all right? Watch this!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Hmm... Still, this is strange...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Hmm... Still, this is strange...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: What? You grow a third nut or something?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What? You grow a third nut or something?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: If only! But no, I'm referring to Lady One.{LF}She was said to be in the Cathedral City.{LF}Why would she come to this place?{#Name="Octa"}
source: If only! But no, I'm referring to Lady One.{LF}She was said to be in the Cathedral City.{LF}Why would she come to this place?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Don't know, don't care.{LF}Leave the thinkin' to the eggheads.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Don't know, don't care.{LF}Leave the thinkin' to the eggheads.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ugh, again? These jerks are freakin' obnoxious!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Ugh, again? These jerks are freakin' obnoxious!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Takes one to know one...{#Name="Dito"}
source: Takes one to know one...{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Come again!?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Come again!?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Just kidding! Kidding! Hoooooo...{#Name="Dito"}
source: Just kidding! Kidding! Hoooooo...{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Huh? Wait...huh? Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Huh? Wait...huh? Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What? Stop babbling like an idiot{LF}and tell me what you want.{#Name="Zero"}
source: What? Stop babbling like an idiot{LF}and tell me what you want.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero!? Zeeero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero!? Zeeero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: WHAT!? Are you deaf or just dumb!?{#Name="Zero"}
source: WHAT!? Are you deaf or just dumb!?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Helloooooo? Zero? I can't hear you!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Helloooooo? Zero? I can't hear you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I don't know where you are anymore, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I don't know where you are anymore, Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: ...Wait, what?{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...Wait, what?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Perhaps this forest is affecting{LF}his ability to sense you...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Perhaps this forest is affecting{LF}his ability to sense you...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: ゼロ様。私、すごぉおいコト、{LF}わかっちゃったんですけどぉ{#Name="セント"}
source: ゼロ様。私、すごぉおいコト、{LF}わかっちゃったんですけどぉ{#Name="セント"}

translation: まっ、こんなこと、{LF}私くらいの者しかひらめけないと思いますけどぉお{#Name="セント"}
source: まっ、こんなこと、{LF}私くらいの者しかひらめけないと思いますけどぉお{#Name="セント"}

translation: 前置きはいいよ。何？{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 前置きはいいよ。何？{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: くふふっ。ここはですね、宝箱を取るとォ……{#Name="セント"}
source: くふふっ。ここはですね、宝箱を取るとォ……{#Name="セント"}

translation: なんとっ、木の葉が１枚落ちるんですよぉおお{#Name="セント"}
source: なんとっ、木の葉が１枚落ちるんですよぉおお{#Name="セント"}

translation: 違う。宝箱を取ると、アンデッドが出てくるんだ{#Name="ディト"}
source: 違う。宝箱を取ると、アンデッドが出てくるんだ{#Name="ディト"}

translation: たしかにさっきから……{#Name="デカート"}
source: たしかにさっきから……{#Name="デカート"}

translation: 私も気づいておりました{#Name="オクタ"}
source: 私も気づいておりました{#Name="オクタ"}

translation: ……わ、私もぉお気づいてたしぃい{#Name="セント"}
source: ……わ、私もぉお気づいてたしぃい{#Name="セント"}

translation: つまり、コイツらは単体だと{LF}引きの弱いバーターってことか。雑魚がッ！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: つまり、コイツらは単体だと{LF}引きの弱いバーターってことか。雑魚がッ！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You thought...{#Name="Zero"}
source: You thought...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: This would kill me?{#Name="Zero"}
source: This would kill me?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: WELL, THINK AGAIN!{#Name="Zero"}
source: WELL, THINK AGAIN!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Goodness... So that's how they regenerate...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Goodness... So that's how they regenerate...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Zero? Zero, what happened!? Are you okay?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero? Zero, what happened!? Are you okay?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: So what? The big dummy was{LF}able to sense Zero's pain?{#Name="Dito"}
source: So what? The big dummy was{LF}able to sense Zero's pain?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Such an intense bond...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Such an intense bond...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Hey, guys? Now's our chance.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Hey, guys? Now's our chance.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Our chance for what?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Our chance for what?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Uh, if you hadn't noticed, Zero's a bit{LF}tied up at the moment. She can't use{LF}her crazy powers or any of that junk.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Uh, if you hadn't noticed, Zero's a bit{LF}tied up at the moment. She can't use{LF}her crazy powers or any of that junk.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Now's our chance to haul ass outta here!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Now's our chance to haul ass outta here!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Well...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Well...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: That's one possibility...{#Name="Octa"}
source: That's one possibility...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Mmm... I suppose it might work?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Mmm... I suppose it might work?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: You suppose wrong, assholes!{#Name="Zero"}
source: You suppose wrong, assholes!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Where are you going, Mikhail?{LF}Lady Zero needs you!{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Where are you going, Mikhail?{LF}Lady Zero needs you!{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Gonna run off and piss yourself, are ya?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Gonna run off and piss yourself, are ya?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I'm not running! And I'm not pissing myself,{LF}either! Not yet, anyway...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm not running! And I'm not pissing myself,{LF}either! Not yet, anyway...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Are you okay!?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Are you okay!?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Just hurry up and pull it out!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Just hurry up and pull it out!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Now THERE'S a sorry sight!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Now THERE'S a sorry sight!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: You say something?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You say something?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Who, me? N-No! Nothing at all!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Who, me? N-No! Nothing at all!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: It's Zero! She's here! The traitor is here!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: It's Zero! She's here! The traitor is here!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Protect us, Lady Three! Please!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Protect us, Lady Three! Please!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: There's something weird going on in this forest.{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: There's something weird going on in this forest.{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Who cares? Kill her!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Who cares? Kill her!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: If this keeps up... Lady Three will... Uuurgh...{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: If this keeps up... Lady Three will... Uuurgh...{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Get up, old man!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Get up, old man!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Shit... My whole body's itchy as hell!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Shit... My whole body's itchy as hell!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: We can't fight like this...{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: We can't fight like this...{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: What the hell is happening!?{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: What the hell is happening!?{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: This is bad! How'd she get this far!?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: This is bad! How'd she get this far!?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: See!? I told you our defensive positions weren't—{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: See!? I told you our defensive positions weren't—{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Just shut up and fight, idiot!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Just shut up and fight, idiot!{#Name="Soldier G"}
